{"tid":1044632,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"FIFA20封面人物投票 武磊上榜！！！","createTime":"2019-03-03T05:04:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T15:26:13.000Z","uid":1369,"like":40,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"89399bb196e4fcc83b41e4a7f65590e3ed08dcb6","tid":1044632,"uid":1369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T05:04:06.000Z","msg":"FIFA 20封面人物的投票正在火熱進行中，中國球星武磊也進入了候選名單。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/130250_cdd2a23e665c9da2b964f153e0fbd8fa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F130250_cdd2a23e665c9da2b964f153e0fbd8fa.png&h=fcd54ebc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武磊在今年1月從上海上港加盟了愛斯賓奴，登陸西甲後，武磊表現出色，在昨晚愛斯賓奴主場3-1擊敗華拉度列的西甲比賽，武磊更是收穫了自己在愛斯賓奴的首粒進球。<br />\n<br />\n自從登陸西甲後，武磊的名氣越來越高，現在FIFA 20也把他放到了封面人物的投票候選名單中。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/130331_6235e96dd2559f37fbeb9fac6c734261.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F130331_6235e96dd2559f37fbeb9fac6c734261.png&h=5be3e0ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n目前武磊在投票中排名第九，而排名第一的是南韓球星孫興慜，緊隨其後的是C朗拿度和美斯。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/130357_9eceaf17eb64e07c7c4275ad46023e0a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F130357_9eceaf17eb64e07c7c4275ad46023e0a.png&h=280dfde7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"79f08bbb7589bc51019c6445dd55be8e4d39e6d3","tid":1044632,"uid":236414,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T05:05:22.000Z","msg":"sb"},{"pid":"038bdb6345aae4d75e937d3c5084af1a2d25f759","tid":1044632,"uid":135957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03